<header>
    <div class="logo">uFlu? </div>
    <span id="header-message">"Hope you feel better soon!"</span>
</header>

<div id="container-fluid" class="desk-bg">

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-2"></div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="result-message">
                <div class="message-logo">uFlu? </div>
                <div class="result-text">Hi!&nbsp <span id="user-name">{{name}}</span>, <br>
                    Based on your symptoms, you might have <span id="diagnosis-result">{{severity}}.</span> <br>
                    Below is a list of recommended items to help you feel more comfortable. <br>
                    <span id="items">{{cureList}}.</span><br>
                    We suggest that you get some medication. Here is a map <div id="walgreens-links">{{drugstoreLink}}</div>of
                    some nearby
                    Walgreens locations in your area. <br>
                    Also, if you can't contact your family doctor, try <a href="https://www.teladoc.com/">Teladoc
                    </a>.
                    <br>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-2"></div>
    </div>

</div>